PUSH UP COUNTER PROJECT:

PHASE 1: TRAINING PHASE:
Training on Kaggle model YOLO11n-POSE from Ultralytics with Dataset COCO-POSE.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
PHASE 2: RUNNING PHASE: 
Step 1. python -m venv venv + venv\Scripts\activate (Windows) - Set up Venv for Python

Step 2. pip install opencv-python numpy ultralytics  (installed after activate virtual environment)

Step 3. Run model with 1 in 3 command:

Chạy bằng webcam.    
python pushup_counter.py --source 0 --output output.mp4

Chạy với source Video
python pushup_counter.py --source path/to/video.mp4 --output output.mp4

Chạy không GUI
python pushup_counter.py --source 0 --output output.mp4 --no-gui
